name: [C4] LOADING LEVEL - ID:G14
description:
LOADING LEVEL… is an artpiece created by Engwind displaying a Cyber Crew Clone in the ZONE. He’s ready to go in whatever direction or planet he is needed.
Geared up and ready to go!

LOADING LEVEL... is a collaboration between ENGWIND and the amazing DJ from Miami PLS&TY who has made custom music and sound design for the artwork. PLS&TY and ENGWIND have a long history together creating graphics for Bitcoin, LAYER3 and more…

Note: this is an art piece first and foremost, however, in the future we may plan to reward collectors of limited edition pieces like this one.

description:
An artpiece crafted from 10 of the BADDEST worlds of ENGWIND. For the last 4 years ENGWIND has been creating MASSIVE  futuristic environments using the UE4 game engine. Featured  in this piece is a CYBER CLONE traveling through all these distant and detailed worlds. With the CYBER CLONE there is an endless amount of  worlds to be explored.

name: [C4] CYBER CLONE - ID:G09
description:
Over a period lasting several months, the Cyber Crew Forge has been observed using up vast amounts of power. The owner, the ever secretive Gauge,  has been developing a sophisticated and extremely tech-centric project that’s been absorbing his full attention.

The Cyber Crew Clone 
C3||Atom-regeneration Slayer-6 model

Cyber Clones will  be METAVERSE-READY 3D rigged playable characters. This means you can import them into ANY compatible metaverse or game. You will also get all the 3D files and licenses to your individual PFP. All clones will also come with a lifetime subscription to Gauges Cyber Subscription (owner only!).

Gauge @ the Cyber Forge has done it again!
Note: This special item has increased utility that will qualify its owner to exclusive Airdrops and perks.
All the newest Crew Clones come with a  "Gauge's Gear and Mayhem Subscription" for weapons and wearables. For every new ROUND of Cyber Crew, members will get one or more FREE limited weapon(s) or wearable(s). 

Additional info on the Subscription:

Gauge develops the best gear in Cybercity and anyone who works the front lines knows his stuff is tops. 

Ex. For Cybercrew Round 5, if Gauge makes a new gun, item, skin, or vehicle, you will get it delivered free of charge!

“If you ain’t equipped with the latest gear from the Cyber Forge, you ain’t a real pro.” -Gauge

name: [C4] CAN-D - ID:G13
description:
An affectionate name for such an efficient killing device.
Everybody these days has some sort of electronic device; be you a robot, or a PRO decked out with the latest Cyber enhancements , your worlds’ gonna get flatlined when this thing gets thrown your way.

Controlled Attack Network-Device

 It’s   named “Candy” because everyone’s gotta have it and you throw it out to all the boys and girls. The more technically inclined will scoff because “you can’t control attack a local network anymore”. Or so they thought…

Gauge is a Maestro of destruction and his specialized Nano-tower-splits  on the CAN-D will create and mimic an existing local network before it implements a multi level  DdoS attack. All this happens while simultaneously Trojanning (it’s a word trust me) a fast learning neural interface that will encapsulate ANY A.I. in an impenetrable and inescapable mirrorverse.

TLDR;? “This thing’ll blow some freakin’ gaskets!”

Note: This item has increased utility that includes cross-platform interoperability, exclusive Airdrops, perks and includes  AAA video game quality 3D Models/Files.

name: [C4] CYBER CYCLE - ID:G11
description:
Faster than light travel?
A myth, however, this thing gets pretty damn close on an open road. Can you really call it a cycle without wheels?
Yes.
 0-100mph in 1.5s
(that’s 160.98* km for all you more worldly people…)
Overkill? You bet!
Fun as hell? That’s right.
Aggressively and stupidly stylish?
Heyyy, you are getting the hang of this!

The ultimate Cybercity vehicle.

Gauge… please stop… enough is enough, said no one ever!

Note: This item has increased utility that includes cross-platform interoperability, exclusive Airdrops, perks and includes  AAA video game quality 3D Models/Files.

name: [C4] CHROME CANNON - ID:G08
description:
An aptly named micro-railgun, part quantum fission propulsion mixed with  just a smidge of nanotech. This  breathtaking instrument of death has “Obscene Levels of  Propulsion”. Tech with a unique nanite-course correction aiming ability that makes for  an unmatched level of precision. 

Gauge from the Cybercrew Forge crafted these in limited quantities  then destroyed the blueprints, Making  these an extremely sought after piece of equipment.

Note From The Crew:
These Limited edition NFT items come as assets fully rigged and ready for import into any Metaverse game or world. You also get full rights to your items  within reason, however, we maintain the right to remove said use if it is deemed detrimental to the brand or image at any point now or in the future .

We probably won’t but just don’t do anything stupid or illegal is all we are saying.
